      • getItemTag

        public static java.lang.Object getItemTag(org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack item,
                                          java.lang.Object... keys)
        Gets an NBT tag in a given item with the specified keys
        Parameters:
        item - The itemstack to get the keys from
        keys - The keys to fetch; an integer after a key value indicates that it should get the nth place of the previous compound because it is a list;
        Returns:
        The item represented by the keys, and an integer if it is showing how long a list is.

      • setItemTag

        public static org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack setItemTag(org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack item,
                                                        java.lang.Object value,
                                                        java.lang.Object... keys)
        Sets an NBT tag in an item with the provided keys and value
        Parameters:
        item - The itemstack to set
        keys - The keys to set, String for NBTCompound, int or null for an NBTTagList
        value - The value to set
        Returns:
        A new ItemStack with the updated NBT tags
